WEBVTT

00:00.010 --> 00:01.710
'Previously on Broadchurch.'

00:01.760 --> 00:03.750
She says she forgives you...

00:03.800 --> 00:05.150
about the pendant.

00:05.200 --> 00:08.230
Why would I kill a 12-year-old girl?

00:08.280 --> 00:10.430
Why was her pendant
found in your vehicle?

00:10.480 --> 00:15.870
My DS was taking that bagged
evidence... back to HQ.

00:15.920 --> 00:18.070
And... her car was broken into.

00:18.120 --> 00:20.670
~ There's grounds for reopening the case.
~ Don't do this.

00:20.720 --> 00:22.430
Oh, God. You're his wife.

00:22.480 --> 00:26.310
I can't go on meeting you here, mate. People
will start getting the wrong idea.

00:26.360 --> 00:29.070
~ What are you doing here?
~ I want to give evidence.

00:29.120 --> 00:31.430
You want me to go in the
witness box, don't you?

00:31.480 --> 00:33.470
Honestly? I'm torn.

00:33.520 --> 00:36.670
You said yourself, somebody needs
to speak up for Dan. Well...

00:36.720 --> 00:39.920
I'm his dad. It should
be down to me, you know?

00:40.080 --> 00:42.510
Thorp AgriServices.
What is it they do?

00:42.560 --> 00:45.430
Services to the
agricultural industries.

00:48.600 --> 00:50.310
Oh, God, it's a furnace.

00:50.360 --> 00:53.230
Do you still think
Lisa Newbery's alive?

00:55.000 --> 01:01.074
